<br />
LIBRA project (Milan, Italy), http://www.aequilibra.it/; Banca Etica (Padova, Italy),
http://www.bancaetica.com/; Chiemgauer (Bavaria, Germany), http://www.chiemgauer.info/ ; WIR Bank
(Switzerland), http://www.wir.ch/<br />
<br />
